il-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSUUvLG.jpg&h=b834a88e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裊裊亭亭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VcyMi2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VcyMi2.jpg&h=e2913b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盈盈佇立<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HG17QLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHG17QLJ.jpg&h=bf502d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝支持<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqbDc0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqbDc0A.jpg&h=e8af002c&s={SIZE}\" /></p></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6bd9e5dcb9e9b253262f427493ec1ba38cd22edf","tid":2124381,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">貴為人大既阿蛆仍熱心效忠中共，維護香港穩定發展，幫手度掂基本法<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vX4K419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvX4K419.jpg&h=fbb5de32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲好關心香港政治添<br />\n為咗選出欣賞粵劇嘅特首,<br />\n不惜向林鄭投懷送抱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohzdXSLfLZvZDFpV6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohzdXSLfLZvZDFpV6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2cb5d57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪阿姐怒插港獨壞分子 <br />\n苦心勸他們離開香港 <br />\n勿阻香港繁榮穩定發展<br />\n「唔係中國人, 就滾出中國!!!」<br />\n「你係中國人 呢度係中國土地 如果你唔想做中國人&nbsp;咪移民去第二度囉！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9GtkBCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9GtkBCH.jpg&h=8ce8597f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/28192338/image14723